summary: Beautiful Aziraphale by the talented @moistureman, one of our mods!  Do you love Good Omens? Want to shout about it with other...
body:
Beautiful Aziraphale by the talented @moistureman, one of our mods!

Do you love Good Omens? Want to shout about it with other fans and make new friends? Have you fallen in love with Michael Sheen?  

Tea at the Ritz is an LGBT+ safe discord server for fans of Good Omens. Everyone is welcome, old and new fans alike! Come share memes, headcanons, fanart, fanfiction, or just talk about your daily life.

Most importantly… we have Good Omens emojis. 

What are you waiting for? 

Message the admins @saxonvoter, @kationi, or mod @lipwigvonmoist for an invite!
